config DEVICE_MODULES_VIRTIO_VDMABUF
	tristate "DMA-BUF vdmabuf"
	depends on HYPER_VM_UOS
	help
	  Choose this option to enable  vdmabuf feature.
	  vdmabuf is a means of cross-domain shared memory. Its function is
	  to transfer the dmabuf requested by the guest to the host so that
	  both ends can access the same physical mem. This is the
	  configuration of vdmabuf on the guest side.
